summary:
Career goals I thrive to achieve are continuous improvement of my hydro-modeling skills, and impactful scientific research. However, I also want to learn about management and business models used in the industry. 

I am persistent, commited, analytical, detail-oriented, and able problem solver. Besides, I am a fast learner, and can be a constructive team player.
